[tb_start_text mode=3]
In the calm lighting of a restaurant that was not crowded due to it being just past lunchtime, the girl with her black hair tied into two cute pigtails sat quietly in her chair and replied. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3]
"Let's start with a light snack. Both of us could use a bit more time to settle down." [r]
"You're right." [l][r]
